{"tid":1613874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家記唔記得？關於嗰間深藍舖頭呢…","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T16:31:21.000Z","uid":89898,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e4951353a43eca84a9fd6b65fc2aef4ec2a15cb4","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:52:54.000Z","msg":"和理非 &rarr; Deadline &rarr; 勇武嘅循環<br />\n<br />\n和理非咁罷住食同時出公開信，要求某個限期之前﹙例如3日內﹚，某啲支那藍店做到啲乜，做唔到就再升級。咁係咪解決到出師有冇名嘅問題？<br />\n<br />\n例如要求吉野家出聲名承認打壓良心員工、post返張撕紙狗出嚟譴責魔警暴力；例如要求美心有實權嘅高層出嚟，表達對美心太子女扭曲事實、誣蔑示威者、打壓學生嘅不滿；例如要求福建360解釋佢地高層同白衫佬嘅關係，要佢地聲明割席&hellip;等等等等<br />\n<br />\n個deadline要求實質係乜，當然唔重要，我亦都預期啲垃圾商家佬唔會認真應。但係呢個deadline係畀咗和理非一個做文宣嘅機會。去嗰啲鋪頭門口貼晒啲公開信，中英對照圖文並茂，解釋佢哋做過啲乜嘢，畀佢哋公司壓力又好、外國傳媒影相又好、淺黃中立知道又好。<br />\n<br />\n3日限期一到，咁就係你教我和平表達訴求冇用，咁就出師有名，同時畀到更多冇咁上心嘅普通市民知，「嘩係喎starbucks係個仆街美心太子女嘅家當嚟㗎喎」「等我都一齊罷食吉野家先」。文宣效果，對內對外、對其他商家都更大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s. 想問一句，點樣justify到打中銀但係金拱門咩事都冇？因為商業性質唔同？明明都係送錢上支那㗎&hellip;&hellip;定因為開24搞唔到？學術討論"},{"pid":"20cf62f142eca1acc8fbb838c82933e05ba6beb6","tid":1613874,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"McDonald is not fully Chinese money there is still significant portion owned by local or foreign investors unlike BOC"},{"pid":"f44e8a6dd7a4b0c6e2abe3876283b5f3cabb70ae","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"呢個提議係睇完之前啲手足嘅post諗嘅。3日文宣deadline，正正係畀手足整理返有咩證據、證明唔止係立場問題、畀足有理由對方糾正唔同程度嘅錯誤，出師有名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《嗱..各位係時間冷靜啦,爆地鐵ok,爆藍色店舖就唔好啦,政見不合就爆人唔係我地應有行為》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1613564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1613564/page/1</a><br />\n《破壞商舖請合乎比例原則》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1613194/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1613194/page/1</a><br />\n《攪咩商家都要有齊證據》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1613783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1613783/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d50ea3f34ee593757a5bc719d087d76455481c0d","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"43dbd6fd35ac7d472b3481e7babfc48c03e12e74","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"9c912613abcb6473120f10c60514eca9aef637ac","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:59:01.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"a4b12cdbe0e413b50fcc550305f229736c084dd0","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"80c8bcc7754edf400d5cc5c4bd722ebc124dfdb6","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:59:27.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"8dc6bf352433e0929e07da616fbf2015480edd54","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"e20a4a87cbd7a9150f876259ddc44537da67b07c","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:00:05.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"50943c0b176c3c7e541541f984418163ec665d8c","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"推8"},{"pid":"e8f7c5d36ba2abd71433c6a82aaf97ef6f73c80c","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:00:28.000Z","msg":"推9"},{"pid":"d4a89fb5c5b025d38f7a42c29ff084fafec40cb3","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"4980b153f73376e484ea0421319554629e51e397","tid":1613874,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"可以<br />\n跪地道歉就放過佢"},{"pid":"87d9a5dc3d4c041e2511a082852eb0934bb81cb0","tid":1613874,"uid":89898,"like":0,